org.slf4j.impl

Class StaticLoggerBinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.slf4j.impl.StaticLoggerBinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.slf4j.spi.LoggerFactoryBinder

    public final class StaticLoggerBinder
extends Object
implements org.slf4j.spi.LoggerFactoryBinder
    The static binder for slf4j logging, which allows CAS to select its own ILoggerFactory instance at runtime. Note that this class MUST reside in the org.slf4j.impl package so it can be loaded by the runtime dynamic lookup.
    Since:
    4.1.0
    Author:
    Misagh Moayyed
